         <abstract id="aspace_b94d350caacafc47c618173acac70b26">Lawyer and philanthropist of
            Peekskill, N.Y. Personal, business, political, and philanthropic correspondence (chiefly
            1925-1938), relating to Pugsley's political work for the Democratic Party, his
